# Running-Works.io
# Running works is a company that offers a selection of used housed with home automation. 
  Their target audience is college students. 
  They want to convey a sense of wonder, while at the same time being down-to-earth.

#JOB DESCRIPTION
# To create a website that mainly provide customer support for the company. The goal is to increase sales. Besides the landing page, the website will need a about page, shop page and blog.   The landing page should have a Our Values section  There should be a call to action to get users to call for more information. They would prefer a old-fashioned design, and would like      you to use the brand color, which is purple. Take into account the client's preferences and values.

#DEADLINE
#6 Days.
